{"tid":1529560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家啲輔助技能無升級到？","createTime":"2019-09-01T18:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T18:24:11.000Z","uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6f277c68a5c2d35a7ef112e2bdcc1c1445765d","tid":1529560,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:22:38.000Z","msg":"我哋而家嘅戰線唔單只係黑警 <br />\n仲要加埋刀手同白衫廢老<br />\n但大家自從612之後就喺防護裝備上不斷提升<br />\n反而遺忘左輔助工具 技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep0G7QL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep0G7QL.jpg&h=9d5a08a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波子<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></strong></span><br />\n大家唔好睇小呢啲波子<br />\n其實當敵方追緊埋嚟嘅時候<br />\n將大量嘅波子揼落地下/拋向敵方嘅時候<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">一地嘅波子有效降低佢嘅跑速 分散佢嘅注意力<br />\n增加我方逃跑時間 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgkjUxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgkjUxv.jpg&h=268dda80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡椒粉<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span></strong><br />\n古語有云你有張良計我有過牆梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有胡椒噴霧我都有胡椒粉<br />\n相信大家食嘢嘅時候都有落胡椒粉<br />\n稍微落得多少少隔離嗰個都咳到仆街<br />\n所以當有時候需要令到一個人盡快失去行動能力<br />\n潑粉落佢塊面度 已經K.O.<br />\n若果想將佢變成遠程攻擊 就可以加上水彈<br />\n喺水入邊加胡椒粉 然後拋擲<br />\n<br />\n以下只屬個人微見 諗法 <br />\n集思廣益 希望將更多嘅輔助技能升到頂級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保持憤怒 唔好忘記烈士義士嘅犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可</span></strong>"},{"pid":"71f900688ef8b4b4c1f2d47272e2b3f82ed73113","tid":1529560,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:23:00.000Z","msg":"無可能831咁大件事都無風聲！<br />\n<br />\n推上去熱門<br />\n<br />\n《太子真相》一句到尾，有無黃絲黨鐵職員出黎講咩事？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529489</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39aa374db33678f16c0c801790d908e647c38d19","tid":1529560,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:24:11.000Z","msg":"彩彈啦 個debuff耐D"}]}